divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside when i looked up and saw 3 flying objects(which had 2 large balls at the end of them that shined a very bright light) and i thought they were airplanes but they where traveling at the same speed next to eachother and then a 4th flying object came out of knowwhere and flew next to the rest of them, then they formed a square and stayed in the same posistion for few minutes then all flew off in different directions.
